# * check accounts
# ** 1. check accounts succeeds when all accounts are declared
<
account a
2020-01-01
  (a)  1
$ hledger -f- check accounts

# ** 2. and otherwise fails:
<
2020-01-01
  (a)  1
$ hledger -f- check accounts
>2 /account "a" has not been declared/
>=1

# ** 3. also fails for forecast accounts
<
commodity $
account a
~ 2022-01-31
    a  $1
    b

$ hledger -f- --today 2022-01-01 --forecast check accounts
>2 /account "b" has not been declared/
>=1

# ** 4. also fails in --strict mode
$ hledger -f- --today 2022-01-01 --forecast --strict bal
>2 /account "b" has not been declared/
>=1

# ** 5. also fails for auto accounts
<
commodity $
account a

= a
  (b)    $1

2022-01-31
    (a)  $1

2022-02-01
$ hledger -f- --auto check accounts
>2 /account "b" has not been declared/
>=1

# ** 6. also fails in --strict mode
$ hledger -f- --auto --strict bal
>2 /account "b" has not been declared/
>=1

# ** 7. The default conversion accounts used by --infer-equity (and the parent accounts, and children) are automatically recognised by check accounts.
<
account a
account b

2024-01-01
  a    1A
  b   -1B

2024-01-01
  ; all of these are auto-recognised
  equity:conversion              0
  equity:conversion:A-B          0
  equity:conversion:A-B:A        0
  equity:conversion:A-B:B        0
  equity:conversion:foo:bar:baz  0

$ hledger -f- check accounts --infer-equity

# ** 8. When the base conversion account has been customised, --infer-equity's conversion accounts are still automatically recognised.
<
account a
account b
account equity:trade  ; type:V

2024-01-01
  a    1A
  b   -1B

2024-01-01
  ; all of these are auto-recognised
  equity:trade:A-B          0
  equity:trade:A-B:A        0
  equity:trade:A-B:B        0
  equity:trade:foo:bar:baz  0

$ hledger -f- check accounts

# ** 8. When the base conversion account has been customised, the default conversion account is no longer automatically recognised.
<
account a
account b
account equity:trade  ; type:V

2024-01-01
  equity:conversion        0

$ hledger -f- check accounts
>2 /"equity:conversion" has not been declared/
>=1
